<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />
  <title>About - Blogs by Dagem</title>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

  <div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
          <h1 class="display-4 mb-3">About Me</h1>
          <p class="lead text-muted">Passionate about technology, AI, and sharing knowledge!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-4">
            <img src="/images/IMG_8186.jpg" class="rounded-circle" style="width: 150px; height: 150px; object-fit: cover;" alt="Dagem's Profile Picture">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-8">
            <h2>Dagem</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">Full Stack Developer</p>
            <p>I am a full stack developer with a passion for building web applications. I am a quick learner and I am always looking to improve my skills.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="my-5">
          <div class="col-md-12 mb-4">
            <h3>My Mission</h3>
            <p>My mission is to build web applications that are user-friendly and efficient. I want to create web applications that are easy to use and understand.</p>
            <p>I also want to create applications that can help people in their daily lives.</p>
          </div>
        <hr class="my-5">

        <div class="text-center">
          <h3>Get in Touch</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mb-4">Interested in collaborating or just want to say hello? I'd love to hear from you!</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Me</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>
</body>
</html>
